    "text": "Many thanks Robert for the great channel. Really love to see your passion and joy :)\nRegarding the Mechanism, \nI wonder whether the input rotation to the output linear motion has a 1:1 ratio, and it is probably harmonic motion where x=2Rcos(θ). This should be taken into account when programming the controller. \nGood luck!",
